var book = {
	"name": "Micah",
	"numChapters": 7,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22581A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22581A\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which came <i>to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22581B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22581B\"></sup>Micah of Moresheth in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22581C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22581C\"></sup>Jotham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22581D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22581D\"></sup>Ahaz <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22581E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22581E\"></sup>Hezekiah, kings of Judah, which he saw concerning Samaria and Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hear, O peoples, all of you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22582F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22582F\"></sup>Listen, O earth and all it contains,And let the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22582G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22582G\"></sup>witness against you,The Lord from His holy temple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22583H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22583H\"></sup>coming forth from His place.He will come down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22583I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22583I\"></sup>tread on the high places of the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22584J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22584J\"></sup>The mountains will melt under HimAnd the valleys will be split,Like wax before the fire,Like water poured down a steep place.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>All this is for the rebellion of JacobAnd for the sins of the house of Israel.What is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22585K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22585K\"></sup>rebellion of Jacob?Is it not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22585L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22585L\"></sup>Samaria?What is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22585M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22585M\"></sup>high place of Judah?Is it not Jerusalem?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I will make Samaria a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22586N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22586N\"></sup>heap of ruins in the open country,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22586O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22586O\"></sup>Planting places for a vineyard.I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22586P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22586P\"></sup>pour her stones down into the valleyAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22586Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22586Q\"></sup>lay bare her foundations.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22587R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22587R\"></sup>idols will be smashed,All of her earnings will be burned with fireAnd all of her images I will make desolate,For she collected <i>them</i> from a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22587S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22587S\"></sup>harlot’s earnings,And to the earnings of a harlot they will return.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Because of this I must lament and wail,I must go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22588T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22588T\"></sup>barefoot and naked;I must make a lament like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22588U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22588U\"></sup>jackalsAnd a mourning like the ostriches.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22589V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22589V\"></sup>wound is incurable,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22589W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22589W\"></sup>it has come to Judah;It has reached the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22589X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22589X\"></sup>gate of my people,<i>Even</i> to Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22590Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22590Y\"></sup>Tell it not in Gath,Weep not at all.At Beth-le-aphrah roll yourself in the dust.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Go on your way, inhabitant of Shaphir, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22591Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22591Z\"></sup>shameful nakedness.The inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22591AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22591AA\"></sup>Zaanan does not escape.The lamentation of Beth-ezel: “He will take from you its support.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the inhabitant of MarothBecomes weak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22592AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22592AB\"></sup>waiting for good,Because a calamity has come down from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22592AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22592AC\"></sup>gate of Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Harness the chariot to the team of horses,O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22593AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22593AD\"></sup>Lachish—She was the beginning of sinTo the daughter of Zion—Because in you were foundThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22593AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22593AE\"></sup>rebellious acts of Israel.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore you will give parting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22594AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22594AF\"></sup>giftsOn behalf of Moresheth-gath;The houses of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22594AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22594AG\"></sup>Achzib <i>will</i> become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22594AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22594AH\"></sup>deceptionTo the kings of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Moreover, I will bring on youThe one who takes possession,O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22595AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22595AI\"></sup>Mareshah.The glory of Israel will enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22595AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22595AJ\"></sup>Adullam.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Make yourself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22596AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22596AK\"></sup>bald and cut off your hair,Because of the children of your delight;Extend your baldness like the eagle,For they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22596AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22596AL\"></sup>go from you into exile."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22597A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22597A\"></sup>scheme iniquity,Who work out evil on their beds!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22597B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22597B\"></sup>When morning comes, they do it,For it is in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22597C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22597C\"></sup>power of their hands.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22598D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22598D\"></sup>covet fields and then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22598E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22598E\"></sup>seize <i>them</i>,And houses, and take <i>them</i> away.They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22598F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22598F\"></sup>rob a man and his house,A man and his inheritance.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22599G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22599G\"></sup>planning against this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22599H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22599H\"></sup>family a calamityFrom which you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22599I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22599I\"></sup>cannot remove your necks;And you will not walk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22599J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22599J\"></sup>haughtily,For it will be an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22599K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22599K\"></sup>evil time.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“On that day they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22600L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22600L\"></sup>take up against you a tauntAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22600M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22600M\"></sup>utter a bitter lamentation <i>and</i> say,‘We are completely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22600N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22600N\"></sup>destroyed!He exchanges the portion of my people;How He removes it from me!To the apostate He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22600O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22600O\"></sup>apportions our fields.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Therefore you will have no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22601P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22601P\"></sup>stretching a measuring lineFor you by lot in the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22602Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22602Q\"></sup>Do not speak out,’ <i>so</i> they speak out.<i>But if</i> they do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22602R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22602R\"></sup>not speak out concerning these things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22602S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22602S\"></sup>Reproaches will not be turned back.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Is it being said, O house of Jacob:‘Is the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22603T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22603T\"></sup>impatient?Are these His doings?’Do not My words <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22603U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22603U\"></sup>do goodTo the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22603V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22603V\"></sup>walking uprightly?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Recently My people have arisen as an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22604W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22604W\"></sup>enemy—You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22604X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22604X\"></sup>strip the robe off the garmentFrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22604Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22604Y\"></sup>unsuspecting passers-by,<i>From</i> those returned from war.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The women of My people you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22605Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22605Z\"></sup>evict,Each <i>one</i> from her pleasant house.From her children you take My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22605AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22605AA\"></sup>splendor forever.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Arise and go,For this is no place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22606AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22606AB\"></sup>of restBecause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22606AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22606AC\"></sup>uncleanness that brings on destruction,A painful destruction.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“If a man walking after wind and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22607AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22607AD\"></sup>falsehoodHad told lies <i>and said</i>,‘I will speak out to you concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22607AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22607AE\"></sup>wine and liquor,’He would be spokesman to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22607AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22607AF\"></sup>this people.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22608AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22608AG\"></sup>assemble all of you, Jacob,I will surely gather the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22608AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22608AH\"></sup>remnant of Israel.I will put them together like sheep in the fold;Like a flock in the midst of its pastureThey will be noisy with men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The breaker goes up before them;They break out, pass through the gate and go out by it.So their king goes on before them,And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at their head.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>And I said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22610A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22610A\"></sup>Hear now, heads of JacobAnd rulers of the house of Israel.Is it not for you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22610B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22610B\"></sup>know justice?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“You who hate good and love evil,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22611C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22611C\"></sup>tear off their skin from themAnd their flesh from their bones,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22612D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22612D\"></sup>eat the flesh of my people,Strip off their skin from them,Break their bonesAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22612E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22612E\"></sup>chop <i>them</i> up as for the potAnd as meat in a kettle.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22613F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22613F\"></sup>cry out to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,But He will not answer them.Instead, He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22613G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22613G\"></sup>hide His face from them at that timeBecause they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22613H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22613H\"></sup>practiced evil deeds.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the prophets who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22614I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22614I\"></sup>lead my people astray;When they have <i>something</i> to bite with their teeth,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22614J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22614J\"></sup>cry, “Peace,”But against him who puts nothing in their mouthsThey declare holy war.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore <i>it will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22615K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22615K\"></sup>night for you—without vision,And darkness for you—without divination.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22615L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22615L\"></sup>sun will go down on the prophets,And the day will become dark over them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The seers will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22616M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22616M\"></sup>ashamedAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22616N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22616N\"></sup>diviners will be embarrassed.Indeed, they will all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22616O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22616O\"></sup>cover <i>their</i> mouthsBecause there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22616P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22616P\"></sup>no answer from God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On the other hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22617Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22617Q\"></sup>I am filled with power—With the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—And with justice and courageTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22617R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22617R\"></sup>make known to Jacob his rebellious act,Even to Israel his sin.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now hear this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22618S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22618S\"></sup>heads of the house of JacobAnd rulers of the house of Israel,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22618T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22618T\"></sup>abhor justiceAnd twist everything that is straight,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22619U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22619U\"></sup>build Zion with bloodshedAnd Jerusalem with violent injustice.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Her leaders pronounce <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22620V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22620V\"></sup>judgment for a bribe,Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22620W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22620W\"></sup>priests instruct for a priceAnd her prophets divine for money.Yet they lean on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22620X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22620X\"></sup>Is not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in our midst?Calamity will not come upon us.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, on account of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22621Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22621Y\"></sup>Zion will be plowed as a field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22621Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22621Z\"></sup>Jerusalem will become a heap of ruins,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22621AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22621AA\"></sup>mountain of the temple <i>will become</i> high places of a forest."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>And it will come about in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22622A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22622A\"></sup>last daysThat the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22622B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22622B\"></sup>mountain of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Will be established as the chief of the mountains.It will be raised above the hills,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22622C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22622C\"></sup>peoples will stream to it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22623D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22623D\"></sup>Many nations will come and say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22623E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22623E\"></sup>Come and let us go up to the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And to the house of the God of Jacob,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22623F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22623F\"></sup>He may teach us about His waysAnd that we may walk in His paths.”For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22623G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22623G\"></sup>from Zion will go forth the law,Even the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22624H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22624H\"></sup>judge between many peoplesAnd render decisions for mighty, distant nations.Then they will hammer their swords <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22624I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22624I\"></sup>into plowsharesAnd their spears into pruning hooks;Nation will not lift up sword against nation,And never again will they train for war.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Each of them will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22625J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22625J\"></sup>sit under his vineAnd under his fig tree,With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22625K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22625K\"></sup>no one to make <i>them</i> afraid,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22625L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22625L\"></sup>mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has spoken.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Though all the peoples walkEach in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22626M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22626M\"></sup>name of his god,As for us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22626N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22626N\"></sup>we will walkIn the name of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22626O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22626O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God forever and ever.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I will assemble the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22627P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22627P\"></sup>lameAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22627Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22627Q\"></sup>gather the outcasts,Even those whom I have afflicted.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I will make the lame a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22628R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22628R\"></sup>remnantAnd the outcasts a strong nation,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22628S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22628S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will reign over them in Mount ZionFrom now on and forever.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“As for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22629T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22629T\"></sup>tower of the flock,Hill of the daughter of Zion,To you it will come—Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22629U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22629U\"></sup>former dominion will come,The kingdom of the daughter of Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Now, why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22630V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22630V\"></sup>cry out loudly?Is there no king among you,Or has your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22630W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22630W\"></sup>counselor perished,That agony has gripped you like a woman in childbirth?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22631X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22631X\"></sup>Writhe and labor to give birth,Daughter of Zion,Like a woman in childbirth;For now you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22631Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22631Y\"></sup>go out of the city,Dwell in the field,And go to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22631Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22631Z\"></sup>There you will be rescued;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22631AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22631AA\"></sup>There the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will redeem youFrom the hand of your enemies.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“And now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22632AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22632AB\"></sup>many nations have been assembled against youWho say, ‘Let her be polluted,And let our eyes gloat over Zion.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But they do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22633AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22633AC\"></sup>know the thoughts of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And they do not understand His purpose;For He has gathered them like sheaves to the threshing floor.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Arise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22634AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22634AD\"></sup>thresh, daughter of Zion,For your horn I will make ironAnd your hoofs I will make bronze,That you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22634AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22634AE\"></sup>pulverize many peoples,That you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22634AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22634AF\"></sup>devote to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their unjust gainAnd their wealth to the Lord of all the earth."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Now muster yourselves in troops, daughter of troops;They have laid siege against us;With a rod they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22635A\"></sup>smite the judge of Israel on the cheek.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“But as for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22636B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22636B\"></sup>you, Bethlehem Ephrathah,<i>Too</i> little to be among the clans of Judah,From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22636C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22636C\"></sup>you One will go forth for Me to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22636D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22636D\"></sup>ruler in Israel.His goings forth are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22636E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22636E\"></sup>from long ago,From the days of eternity.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22637F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22637F\"></sup>give them <i>up</i> until the timeWhen she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22637G\"></sup>who is in labor has borne a child.Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22637H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22637H\"></sup>remainder of His brethrenWill return to the sons of Israel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And He will arise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22638I\"></sup>shepherd <i>His flock</i>In the strength of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,In the majesty of the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> His God.And they will remain,Because at that time He will be greatTo the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22638J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22638J\"></sup>ends of the earth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22639K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22639K\"></sup>will be <i>our</i> peace.When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22639L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22639L\"></sup>Assyrian invades our land,When he tramples on our citadels,Then we will raise against himSeven shepherds and eight leaders of men.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22640M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22640M\"></sup>shepherd the land of Assyria with the sword,The land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22640N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22640N\"></sup>Nimrod at its entrances;And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22640O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22640O\"></sup>deliver <i>us</i> from the AssyrianWhen he attacks our landAnd when he tramples our territory.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22641P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22641P\"></sup>remnant of JacobWill be among many peoplesLike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22641Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22641Q\"></sup>dew from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22641R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22641R\"></sup>showers on vegetationWhich do not wait for manOr delay for the sons of men.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The remnant of JacobWill be among the nations,Among many peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22642S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22642S\"></sup>Like a lion among the beasts of the forest,Like a young lion among flocks of sheep,Which, if he passes through,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22642T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22642T\"></sup>Tramples down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22642U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22642U\"></sup>tears,And there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22642V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22642V\"></sup>none to rescue.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Your hand will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22643W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22643W\"></sup>lifted up against your adversaries,And all your enemies will be cut off.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“It will be in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22644X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22644X\"></sup>That I will cut off your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22644Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22644Y\"></sup>horses from among youAnd destroy your chariots.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will also cut off the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22645Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22645Z\"></sup>cities of your landAnd tear down all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22645AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22645AA\"></sup>fortifications.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will cut off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22646AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22646AB\"></sup>sorceries from your hand,And you will have fortune-tellers no more.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22647AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22647AC\"></sup>I will cut off your carved imagesAnd your <i>sacred</i> pillars from among you,So that you will no longer bow downTo the work of your hands.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will root out your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22648AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22648AD\"></sup>Asherim from among youAnd destroy your cities.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22649AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22649AE\"></sup>execute vengeance in anger and wrathOn the nations which have not obeyed.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Hear now what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is saying,“Arise, plead your case before the mountains,And let the hills hear your voice.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Listen, you mountains, to the indictment of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And you enduring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22651A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22651A\"></sup>foundations of the earth,Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22651B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22651B\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a case against His people;Even with Israel He will dispute.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22652C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22652C\"></sup>My people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22652D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22652D\"></sup>what have I done to you,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22652E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22652E\"></sup>how have I wearied you? Answer Me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Indeed, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22653F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22653F\"></sup>brought you up from the land of EgyptAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22653G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22653G\"></sup>ransomed you from the house of slavery,And I sent before you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22653H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22653H\"></sup>Moses, Aaron and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22653I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22653I\"></sup>Miriam.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“My people, remember nowWhat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22654J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22654J\"></sup>Balak king of Moab counseledAnd what Balaam son of Beor answered him,<i>And</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22654K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22654K\"></sup>Shittim to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22654L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22654L\"></sup>Gilgal,So that you might know the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22654M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22654M\"></sup>righteous acts of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22655N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22655N\"></sup>With what shall I come to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><i>And</i> bow myself before the God on high?Shall I come to Him with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22655O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22655O\"></sup>burnt offerings,With yearling calves?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> take delight in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22656P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22656P\"></sup>thousands of rams,In ten thousand rivers of oil?Shall I present my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22656Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22656Q\"></sup>firstborn <i>for</i> my rebellious acts,The fruit of my body for the sin of my soul?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22657R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22657R\"></sup>told you, O man, what is good;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22657S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22657S\"></sup>what does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> require of youBut to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22657T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22657T\"></sup>do justice, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22657U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22657U\"></sup>love kindness,And to walk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22657V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22657V\"></sup>humbly with your God?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will call to the city—And it is sound wisdom to fear Your name:“Hear, O tribe. Who has appointed its time?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Is there yet a man in the wicked house,<i>Along with</i> treasures of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22659W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22659W\"></sup>wickednessAnd a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22659X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22659X\"></sup>short measure <i>that is</i> cursed?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Can I justify wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22660Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22660Y\"></sup>scalesAnd a bag of deceptive weights?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For the rich men of <i>the</i> city are full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22661Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22661Z\"></sup>violence,Her residents speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22661AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22661AA\"></sup>lies,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22661AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22661AB\"></sup>tongue is deceitful in their mouth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“So also I will make <i>you</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22662AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22662AC\"></sup>sick, striking you down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22662AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22662AD\"></sup>Desolating <i>you</i> because of your sins.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“You will eat, but you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22663AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22663AE\"></sup>not be satisfied,And your vileness will be in your midst.You will <i>try to</i> remove <i>for safekeeping</i>,But you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22663AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22663AF\"></sup>not preserve <i>anything</i>,And what you do preserve I will give to the sword.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“You will sow but you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22664AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22664AG\"></sup>not reap.You will tread the olive but will not anoint yourself with oil;And the grapes, but you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22664AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22664AH\"></sup>not drink wine.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“The statutes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AI\"></sup>OmriAnd all the works of the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AJ\"></sup>Ahab are observed;And in their devices you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AK\"></sup>walk.Therefore I will give you up for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AL\"></sup>destructionAnd your inhabitants for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AM\"></sup>derision,And you will bear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22665AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22665AN\"></sup>reproach of My people.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Woe is me! For I amLike the fruit pickers, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22666A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22666A\"></sup>grape gatherers.There is not a cluster of grapes to eat,<i>Or</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22666B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22666B\"></sup>first-ripe fig <i>which</i> I crave.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The godly person has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22667C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22667C\"></sup>perished from the land,And there is no upright <i>person</i> among men.All of them lie in wait for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22667D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22667D\"></sup>bloodshed;Each of them hunts the other with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22667E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22667E\"></sup>net.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Concerning evil, both hands do it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22668F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22668F\"></sup>well.The prince asks, also the judge, for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22668G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22668G\"></sup>bribe,And a great man speaks the desire of his soul;So they weave it together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The best of them is like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22669H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22669H\"></sup>briar,The most upright like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22669I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22669I\"></sup>thorn hedge.The day when you post your watchmen,Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22669J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22669J\"></sup>punishment will come.Then their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22669K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22669K\"></sup>confusion will occur.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22670L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22670L\"></sup>trust in a neighbor;Do not have confidence in a friend.From her who lies in your bosomGuard your lips.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22671M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22671M\"></sup>son treats father contemptuously,Daughter rises up against her mother,Daughter-in-law against her mother-in-law;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22671N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22671N\"></sup>A man’s enemies are the men of his own household.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But as for me, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22672O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22672O\"></sup>watch expectantly for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22672P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22672P\"></sup>wait for the God of my salvation.My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22672Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22672Q\"></sup>God will hear me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22673R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22673R\"></sup>Do not rejoice over me, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22673S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22673S\"></sup>my enemy.Though I fall I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22673T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22673T\"></sup>rise;Though I dwell in darkness, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22673U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22673U\"></sup>light for me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will bear the indignation of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Because I have sinned against Him,Until He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22674V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22674V\"></sup>pleads my case and executes justice for me.He will bring me out to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22674W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22674W\"></sup>light,<i>And</i> I will see His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22674X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22674X\"></sup>righteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then my enemy will see,And shame will cover her who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22675Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22675Y\"></sup>said to me,“Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God?”My eyes will look on her;At that time she will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22675Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22675Z\"></sup>trampled downLike mire of the streets.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>It will be</i> a day for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22676AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22676AA\"></sup>building your walls.On that day will your boundary be extended.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It <i>will be</i> a day when they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22677AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22677AB\"></sup>come to youFrom Assyria and the cities of Egypt,From Egypt even to the Euphrates,Even from sea to sea and mountain to mountain.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the earth will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22678AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22678AC\"></sup>desolate because of her inhabitants,On account of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22678AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22678AD\"></sup>fruit of their deeds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22679AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22679AE\"></sup>Shepherd Your people with Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22679AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22679AF\"></sup>scepter,The flock of Your possessionWhich dwells by itself in the woodland,In the midst of a fruitful field.Let them feed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22679AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22679AG\"></sup>Bashan and Gilead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22679AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22679AH\"></sup>As in the days of old.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“As in the days when you came out from the land of Egypt,I will show <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22680AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22680AI\"></sup>you miracles.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22681AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22681AJ\"></sup>will see and be ashamedOf all their might.They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22681AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22681AK\"></sup>put <i>their</i> hand on <i>their</i> mouth,Their ears will be deaf.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22682AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22682AL\"></sup>lick the dust like a serpent,Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22682AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22682AM\"></sup>reptiles of the earth.They will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22682AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22682AN\"></sup>trembling out of their fortresses;To the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God they will come in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22682AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22682AO\"></sup>dreadAnd they will be afraid before You.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Who is a God like You, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22683AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22683AP\"></sup>pardons iniquityAnd passes over the rebellious act of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22683AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22683AQ\"></sup>remnant of His possession?He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22683AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22683AR\"></sup>retain His anger forever,Because He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22683AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22683AS\"></sup>delights in unchanging love.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He will again have compassion on us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22684AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22684AT\"></sup>He will tread our iniquities under foot.Yes, You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22684AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22684AU\"></sup>cast all their sinsInto the depths of the sea.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22685AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22685AV\"></sup>truth to Jacob<i>And</i> unchanging love to Abraham,Which You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22685AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22685AW\"></sup>swore to our forefathersFrom the days of old."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;